Invocation Name: p. s. g. news
des:
PSG news is a skill to provide you news about the Paris-Saint-Germain soccer team.
With this skill, you can ask for:
 - "last game": the last game result
 - "next game": details about the next game
 - "leaderboard": the position in the leaderboard
 - "news": the most recent news 

You can say:

"Alexa, open p. s. g. news"
